text: Vivi-Anne Wassdahl (born 28 February 1932) is a Swedish alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Sweden Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
